nl.sense_os.service.constants

Class SenseStatusCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.sense_os.service.constants.SenseStatusCodes

  • public class SenseStatusCodes
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class that contains constants to map the status preference integer to actual status of the system.

    Example: 
     int status = ServiceStateHelper.getInstance(service).getStatusCode();
 boolean ambience = (status & SenseStatusCode.AMBIENCE) > 0;
    Author:
    Steven Mulder
